{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SCARY MAGIC ZOMBIE is a short first-person horror game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The story is:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Evil scientists have created a SCARY MAGIC ZOMBIE.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You play as a secret spy, who enters the facility, and must collect information about this zombie.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But watch out! The SCARY MAGIC ZOMBIE is extremely dangerous.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be very careful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The gameplay is very simple. You walk through the facility, and use the left mouse click button to open doors and pick up documents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You control the player camera with the mouse, and use the WASD keys to move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The controls are:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">WASD keys for movement</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">mouse movement for camera control</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">left mouse click to interact with game objects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">ESCAPE key to open and close the pause menu</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">TAB key to view the current game objective</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">F key to toggle the flashlight</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game is designed for people who enjoy short, suspenseful, frightening experiences, with a highly immersive atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Average completion time: 10-20 minutes.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273910/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730167212","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273910/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=17301672